  "detailed_description": "Dead Shits is a cartoony platformer with traps, enemies and time pressure in fantasy worlds.<br />\r\nSome levels can be destroyed, so be careful!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAre you ready for a difficult game without extra lifes or convenient spawnpoints?<br />\r\nEach level have a different world to explore, with its own feeling and great music.<br />\r\nYour highscore will be saved for completing the whole game of 10 levels.<br />\r\nSo be prepared for this unique game and try your best!",
  "about_the_game": "Dead Shits is a cartoony platformer with traps, enemies and time pressure in fantasy worlds.<br />\r\nSome levels can be destroyed, so be careful!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAre you ready for a difficult game without extra lifes or convenient spawnpoints?<br />\r\nEach level have a different world to explore, with its own feeling and great music.<br />\r\nYour highscore will be saved for completing the whole game of 10 levels.<br />\r\nSo be prepared for this unique game and try your best!",
